{"tid":1832564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門區會委員會改名：公民權利地區發展委員會（因應民政事務總署建議，此委員會只討論屯門區內公民權利相關事宜）","createTime":"2020-01-21T09:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T09:12:04.000Z","uid":228995,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b85c6d9742d7058befd184c512095bcb059af2","tid":1832564,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n張可森<br />\n12分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n在民政事務署多番阻撓下，屯門區議會剛議決通過本人的動議，將被民政事務署DQ的「公民權利發展委員會」修改名稱為<br />\n<br />\n「公民權利地區發展委員會（因應民政事務總署建議，此委員會只討論屯門區內公民權利相關事宜）」，大家可以簡稱因會。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n簡稱因會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da65f37c57b73163472506e8a5e9952324e517fa","tid":1832564,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"功能組別飲食界登記懶人包 - 燒山<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1832526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1832526</a>"},{"pid":"dee22966b891b95098799e3b20edffa8c44379c6","tid":1832564,"uid":308567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hwmy6gC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwmy6gC.gif&h=40647c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1218816278820835329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1218816278820835329&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=60de2bee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1218816278820835329&h=5e18b4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1218816278820835329</a>"}]}